Employee Name: Lyra Kingsleigh

Progress Level: 0/10

First Steps: Yet to find Footing

Skill Set: Persuasion, Performance, Deception, Perception, Gymnastics

Encounter Type: D

Notes:
The only true socially adept member of the group. Seems to hate when things are quiet, always making some sort of noise. This is likely to make her more visible within the fog. This social aspect might help save her from a few of the troubles the average member of the Acquisitions Team encounters, but it makes it unclear if she is the right fit for the AE.
